97 J ames be ye grace off Gode kinge of Scottis to our sereff off Kincar- dine and his deputis yat now is and yat sall happine to be for ye tyme greting. Forsamekle as in ye actioune and causs mowit betuix ane reverende fathir in Criste Jhone bischope off Brechine on ye ta part and our cousinge Georgo erle off Rothess and lord Lesley on ye toyir part tuichinge ye secunde teindis clamyt be ye said reuerende fathir to be awinge to hyme and his kirk off Brechine off ye said erle of Rothess landis in our warde It is counsalit ws be ye lordis off our counsale that consider- ing ye ressonis and allegatiounis producit befoire oure said counsaile and ye alde rollis registris writtis and euidentis send be tharne in yat mater that we mak ye saide reuerende fayir be contentit and pait of ye secund teinde off ye saide erle of Rothess landis for ye tyme of yar beinge in our handis be ressone off warde the quhilk counsaile is guyde for ye possessioune of ye kirk and to ye sustentatione off ye seruice off Almychtye Gode and we ordane and decernis ye samyne to be execut and fulfillit.
